{"tid":2203235,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【12 港人送中 第 24 日】受委託維權律師：港回歸後「偷越邊境」不應被視為罪行 移送返港處理完全可行","createTime":"2020-09-15T07:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T07:56:54.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1a62e40c52cff3c18846362c2f89db54f6e5a9d8","tid":2203235,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T07:56:54.000Z","msg":"違反港區國安法的「香港故事」成員李宇軒等 12 名港人，疑潛逃台灣時被中國海警截獲，至今關押在深圳鹽田看守所已 24 天。受家屬委託、兩度要求會見當事人被拒的內地維權律師盧思位今日撰文，法理分析港人家屬提出對於罪名、辯護權、程序等問題（見全文轉載）。盧思位指出，12 港人牽涉的「偷越國（邊）境」行為，在港澳回歸後已不應被視為罪行，否則在「一國」原則下無法自圓其說。盧又指，內地與香港的移交問題一直沒有明確法律規定，此前都是按個案處理，兩方均有移交先例，認為將 12 港人移送返香港處理「完全可行」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/12-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E7%AC%AC-24-%E6%97%A5-%E5%8F%97%E5%A7%94%E8%A8%97%E7%B6%AD%E6%AC%8A%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB-%E6%B8%AF%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8%E5%BE%8C-%E5%81%B7%E8%B6%8A%E9%82%8A%E5%A2%83-%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E8%A2%AB%E8%A6%96%E7%82%BA%E7%BD%AA%E8%A1%8C-%E7%A7%BB%E9%80%81%E8%BF%94%E6%B8%AF%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F12-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E7%25AC%25AC-24-%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25A7%2594%25E8%25A8%2597%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E5%2581%25B7%25E8%25B6%258A%25E9%2582%258A%25E5%25A2%2583-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E9%2580%2581%25E8%25BF%2594%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25AE%258C%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25A1%258C%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuZ1eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=17fe75ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F12-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E7%25AC%25AC-24-%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E5%2